OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy,
OL,6,Fpossibly thundery showers will clear
OL,7,Feastwards during the evening. Mostly
OL,8,Fdry overnight, with clear spells.
OL,9,FHowever, a few light showers remain
OL,10,Fpossible, mostly in the west and high
OL,11,Fground. Staying breezy, but a mild
OL,12,Fnight to come.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FA bright morning, with spells
OL,15,Fof sunshine. Increasing risk of
OL,16,Fshowery outbreaks of rain developing
OL,17,Fin the west during the afternoon,
OL,18,Fturning heavy over the hills by the
OL,19,Fevening. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
