OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FStaying unsettled, with a mixture of
OL,7,Fsunny spells and showery rain. Some of
OL,8,Fthe showers could be heavy and
OL,9,Fthundery. Temperatures a little below
OL,10,Fnormal, with some chilly nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
